description:
This is a 9 minute workout called 'Guided Meditation for Anxiety | The Hourglass' from the channel Priory.
The workout falls under Rest/Meditation.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Zen Flow and The Deep Recharge vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: Relieve anxiety with this guided meditation called The Hourglass. 

Written and narrated by Priory Cognitive Analytic Therapy (CAT) Psychotherapist Adele Burdon-Bailey, this 8-minute guided meditation allows you to take a breath from the anxieties of the outside world and look after your wellbeing. 

This meditation is designed to help people relieve symptoms of anxiety. For anyone struggling with their mental health, the Hourglass is the perfect way to unwind.
